          _"Process PayPal Labels"
          "Crops and transforms PDF labels saved from PayPal in a manner which allows them to be printed on half-sheet label paper."
          "Lyle Hanson"
          "2009"
          "January 21, 2009"
          ""
          SF-STRING "Label file" "C:\\USPS_Label.pdf")
